## Emergency Communication Disclaimer

HayatKurtar is designed for emergency communication scenarios and is provided
"AS IS" without warranty. While every effort has been made to ensure reliability,
users should:

1. Always contact official emergency services (911, 112, etc.) when possible
2. Use HayatKurtar as supplementary communication when traditional networks fail
3. Test the application before relying on it in emergency situations
4. Understand that message delivery cannot be guaranteed in all circumstances

The developers and contributors of HayatKurtar are not responsible for any
consequences arising from the use or inability to use this software during
emergency situations.

